PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue authorizing the issue and prescribing the dimensions and designs for the minting of two TWENTY DOLLAR SILVER COINS, one depicting a Lockheed 14 Super Electra aircraft and a gold cameo of Zebulon Lewis Leigh, and the other depicting a Fairchild 71C aircraft and a gold cameo of James A. precis:
Order directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue authorizing the issue and
prescribing the dimensions and designs for the minting of two TWENTY DOLLAR
SILVER COINS, one depicting a Lockheed 14 Super Electra aircraft and a gold
cameo of Zebulon Lewis Leigh, and the other depicting a Fairchild 71C
aircraft and a gold cameo of James A. Richardson, both designed to
commemorate the first fifty years of powered flight in Canada.
